Step 1: Start.
Step 2: Accept String sen.
Step 3: Convert it to uppercase
Step 4: If last character of sen is not '.' and not '?'and not'!' print invalid input and stop.
Step 5: Using split() method convert the sentence into an array.
Step 6: Find reverse of a word.
Step 7: If the word is palindrome skip step 8-10.
Step 8: Using a while loop check if the last letters are repeated
Step 9: If step 8 is true remove the repeated letters.
Step 10: Concatenate the word with the reversed word.
Step 11: Print the new sentence.
Step 12: Stop.
